    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "A great freedom is provided in the college",
          "name": "Alan biju",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "The campus greenery is very beautiful and also the Ambience of the campus is very well",
          "name": "Alan biju",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "All the technical assistance which are provided by the college",
          "name": "Jijin Geo Thomas",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "A big good library with many collections of books and a wide calm full area for study and reading,have atleast 15 internet accessible computers within the Library,canteen is big and neat and affordable food items",
          "name": "Balamuraleekrishna N V",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The pollution free campus is much attractive. The vast flaura and fauna in the campus  is very interesting. Plants of 100s of uears of age is present in the campus.",
          "name": "Jeeva Elizabeth Vince",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The teaching styles also inspired me a lot. Sometimes classes are taken in the open air which help students to have a direct connected with the nature.",
          "name": "Jeeva Elizabeth Vince",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Classes are good and we get correct guidance",
          "name": "MINNA PARVEEN PK",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The architecture of the buildings .it's really vintage and it's built in the 80s .",
          "name": "Sankeerthana",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Course is offering a detailed study on Journalism, mass communication and English literature Which is very good to study on a single go.",
          "name": "MITHRA PRAKASH",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "Provides an opportunity for film production, news reading.",
          "name": "MITHRA PRAKASH",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Lack of technical fest and other entertainments",
          "name": "Jijin Geo Thomas",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Cultural activities and encoragemnt from the college managemnet",
          "name": "Jijin Geo Thomas",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Support from department in extracurricular activities are worst",
          "name": "Balamuraleekrishna N V",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Placement cell are not reaching every Students",
          "name": "Balamuraleekrishna N V",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Canteen is located at one end of the campus. It makes the students hard to come from the other end for lunch during break hours. The distance sometimes bothered us.",
          "name": "Jeeva Elizabeth Vince",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "The gym is one of the worst thing in that campus.",
          "name": "Bilal Mohammed",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Some staffs are rude to students sometimes.",
          "name": "Bilal Mohammed",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Less focus given on sports and physical activities to o students outside the Sports departments",
          "name": "Dijo K Biji",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "Toilet facilities were not good in the beginning but now it has been improved",
          "name": "Abhiram A",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "No hostel facilities for boys who come from far away districts",
          "name": "Abhiram A",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        }
      ]
    },
    "affiliated_to": {
      "name": "MG University, Kottayam"
    }
